    <textarea class="right" spellcheck="false" autocomplete="off">
    ::toc
    Dnd Document!::title
    This is the document format I have been developing. Check it out, we've got:

    * Bullets
      - Nested bullets
        + Really nested bullets
        1. Lists even
    * Tables
    * Inline css tags
    * Auto toc population.

    Awesome::table
