      Is Awesome             | None!
      Nice to look at        |
      Plain text is readable |
      Nicely structure       |
      In document scripting  | Not available in web.
    ::comment
      This is a comment block!

    1. One
    2. Two
    3. Three

    Tree content::md
      For more sophisticated documents, you can have nested blocks.
      Auto-header levels::md
        Headers will be of the appropriate level (aka, h2 then h3, etc.).

